[
  {
    "text": "Coffee?\nYes, thank you.",
    "start": 0.208,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "[COFFEE SPLATTERS]\nTECH: Don't be shy, fellas.\nCome check it out.",
    "start": 1.793,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "[WELCOMING CHIME]",
    "start": 3.92,
    "duration": 1.21
  },
  {
    "text": "[FRANK GRUNTS]",
    "start": 5.171,
    "duration": 1.085
  },
  {
    "text": "Snug.\n[CHUCKLES]",
    "start": 7.507,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "TECH: All electric.",
    "start": 8.633,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "Zero to sixty in 3.1 seconds.",
    "start": 10.093,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "I guess that's good.",
    "start": 12.47,
    "duration": 1.877
  },
  {
    "text": "TECH: Watch this.",
    "start": 14.389,
    "duration": 0.959
  },
  {
    "text": "Car, open doors.",
    "start": 15.39,
    "duration": 2.419
  },
  {
    "text": "[GRUNTS]",
    "start": 17.851,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "Neat trick.\n[CHUCKLES] Now you try.",
    "start": 20.02,
    "duration": 2.335
  },
  {
    "text": "[CAR DOOR PINGING]",
    "start": 22.397,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "Car...",
    "start": 24.107,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "please, close doors.",
    "start": 25.567,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "[GENTLE CHIME]\n[ED GROANING]",
    "start": 27.068,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "[FINGERS CRUNCH]\n[STRAINED SCREAM]",
    "start": 28.528,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey!",
    "start": 31.156,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "Pretty fun, I guess.",
    "start": 32.449,
    "duration": 1.167
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, how about this? Car...",
    "start": 33.658,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "drive forward 30 feet.",
    "start": 35.285,
    "duration": 2.377
  },
  {
    "text": "[FRANK CHUCKLES]",
    "start": 38.413,
    "duration": 1.126
  },
  {
    "text": "[CLATTERING]",
    "start": 41.166,
    "duration": 1.042
  },
  {
    "text": "[ELECTRICITY CRACKLING]",
    "start": 43.585,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "Pretty smooth.\nAll right.",
    "start": 47.547,
    "duration": 2.044
  },
  {
    "text": "[CLANKING]",
    "start": 49.632,
    "duration": 1.752
  },
  {
    "text": "[ALARM BLARING]",
    "start": 53.428,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "Impressive.",
    "start": 55.472,
    "duration": 1.042
  },
  {
    "text": "ED: Hey! Guys?",
    "start": 56.556,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "COP: Freeze!\nDon't--",
    "start": 58.058,
    "duration": 1.334
  },
  {
    "text": "[OFFICERS YELLING]",
    "start": 59.434,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "[GUNSHOTS]",
    "start": 60.56,
    "duration": 1.126
  },
  {
    "text": "I tell you, this place\nis falling apart.",
    "start": 64.147,
    "duration": 2.586
  },
  {
    "text": "I got half a dozen witnesses\nthat place you on the scene.",
    "start": 69.569,
    "duration": 2.836
  },
  {
    "text": "We know you were at the bank!",
    "start": 72.447,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm telling you,\nI wasn't there.",
    "start": 74.657,
    "duration": 2.211
  },
  {
    "text": "[SIGHS IN EXASPERATION]",
    "start": 77.994,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks, Park.",
    "start": 80.121,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "This is quite the rap sheet\nyou've got here.",
    "start": 83.083,
    "duration": 4.129
  },
  {
    "text": "It says you served\n20 years\nfor \"man's laughter.\"",
    "start": 87.253,
    "duration": 3.295
  },
  {
    "text": "Must have been quite the joke.",
    "start": 91.466,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "You mean \"manslaughter\"?",
    "start": 93.093,
    "duration": 1.167
  },
  {
    "text": "[OVER SPEAKERS] Well...",
    "start": 97.764,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "we know your boss\ndidn't want cash.",
    "start": 99.891,
    "duration": 2.044
  },
  {
    "text": "So what was the point\nof the robbery?\nWhat did he want?",
    "start": 101.976,
    "duration": 3.295
  },
  {
    "text": "I... wasn't... there.",
    "start": 105.313,
    "duration": 2.878
  },
  {
    "text": "You think you're so smart.",
    "start": 108.233,
    "duration": 2.252
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, I think my bodycam\nmight tell a different story.",
    "start": 110.527,
    "duration": 4.129
  },
  {
    "text": "Ed?",
    "start": 114.697,
    "duration": 0.835
  },
  {
    "text": "Technology really\nis something.",
    "start": 118.159,
    "duration": 3.295
  },
  {
    "text": "Police Squad is all about\n\"transparency\" these days.",
    "start": 121.496,
    "duration": 3.837
  },
  {
    "text": "[SCATTING ABSENTMINDEDLY]",
    "start": 125.375,
    "duration": 1.877
  },
  {
    "text": "Dispatch, this is Drebin.\n10-7.",
    "start": 129.629,
    "duration": 2.753
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, yeah!",
    "start": 132.465,
    "duration": 1.293
  },
  {
    "text": "A chili dog.",
    "start": 133.8,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "[GROANS]",
    "start": 136.386,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "Mm-hmm!",
    "start": 137.595,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Breakfast of champions.",
    "start": 139.097,
    "duration": 1.752
  },
  {
    "text": "FRANK: And a little\nblack coffee.",
    "start": 140.89,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, you can\nfast-forward a bit.",
    "start": 142.1,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "[FAST-FORWARDING]",
    "start": 144.853,
    "duration": 2.252
  },
  {
    "text": "FRANK: License and\nregistration, please.",
    "start": 147.147,
    "duration": 1.751
  },
  {
    "text": "MAN: Uh...[CLEARS THROAT]",
    "start": 148.94,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh...[CHUCKLES]",
    "start": 151.734,
    "duration": 0.876
  },
  {
    "text": "This isn't mine.",
    "start": 152.652,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "[WET FLATULENCE]\nFRANK: Excuse me.",
    "start": 154.07,
    "duration": 1.877
  },
  {
    "text": "[FARTING CONTINUES]\nFRANK: Oh, boy. Listen, uh,",
    "start": 155.989,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "you seem like a decent fella.",
    "start": 157.866,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm gonna let you off\nwith a warning.\nHave a great day, bye.",
    "start": 159.409,
    "duration": 2.711
  },
  {
    "text": "It's much later in the day.\nFast-forward a while.",
    "start": 162.162,
    "duration": 2.711
  },
  {
    "text": "[FAST-FORWARDING]",
    "start": 164.914,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll see. Just wait.",
    "start": 166.416,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "[STRAINED SIGH]",
    "start": 168.168,
    "duration": 1.584
  },
  {
    "text": "I need a bathroom. Oh, God.",
    "start": 169.794,
    "duration": 2.378
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on, move, move, move!",
    "start": 172.213,
    "duration": 2.211
  },
  {
    "text": "Focus, Frank, focus.",
    "start": 174.507,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "You got this, you got this.",
    "start": 176.885,
    "duration": 2.252
  },
  {
    "text": "[FRANK CRIES OUT,\nMOANS ON MONITOR]",
    "start": 179.179,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "[GRUNTS]",
    "start": 182.056,
    "duration": 0.876
  },
  {
    "text": "Maybe a little more.",
    "start": 182.974,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm gonna ruin another suit!",
    "start": 184.1,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "Barnes!\n[PANICKED GROANING]",
    "start": 185.81,
    "duration": 1.794
  },
  {
    "text": "BARNES: Sorry.",
    "start": 187.645,
    "duration": 0.918
  },
  {
    "text": "[FOOTAGE FAST-FORWARDING]",
    "start": 188.605,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "FRANK: Police business!",
    "start": 189.898,
    "duration": 1.459
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh, there is a line,\nman![SCREAMS]",
    "start": 191.399,
    "duration": 2.377
  },
  {
    "text": "[CUSTOMERS SCREAMING]",
    "start": 193.818,
    "duration": 0.918
  },
  {
    "text": "FRANK: Come on!",
    "start": 198.031,
    "duration": 0.959
  },
  {
    "text": "[FOOTAGE FAST-FORWARDING]",
    "start": 199.991,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "You're disgusting,\nyou stupid idiot.",
    "start": 203.244,
    "duration": 2.628
  },
  {
    "text": "Breastfed until you were 13,\nyou freak.",
    "start": 207.332,
    "duration": 2.752
  },
  {
    "text": "[FOOTAGE FAST-FORWARDING]",
    "start": 210.126,
    "duration": 1.752
  },
  {
    "text": "Can't get it up without\nthe stench of milk\non your chin.",
    "start": 211.92,
    "duration": 3.42
  },
  {
    "text": "[VOICE TREMBLING]\nDon't you dare.",
    "start": 216.758,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't do it. Don't eat it!",
    "start": 218.301,
    "duration": 1.877
  },
  {
    "text": "SUSPECT: Oh, God!\nFrank.",
    "start": 221.221,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "I had five more that day.",
    "start": 223.348,
    "duration": 2.043
  },
  {
    "text": "Feel better, Frank?\nYou better believe it.",
    "start": 225.433,
    "duration": 2.044
  },
  {
    "text": "Mm!\n[FOOTAGE FAST-FORWARDING]",
    "start": 227.56,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]",
    "start": 231.981,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes!",
    "start": 234.4,
    "duration": 1.21
  },
  {
    "text": "That's you inside the bank,\nplain as day.",
    "start": 235.652,
    "duration": 2.752
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, fine.",
    "start": 238.446,
    "duration": 1.084
  }
]